data.description: Nestled on a private cul-de-sac street on the Lowell/Tewksbury line, this home is tailor-made for buyers seeking comfort and convenience! Step inside to discover an open concept main living area that boasts a modern kitchen complete with stainless steel appliances and gas cooking, spacious living room & dining area, and a convenient half bath with laundry. Upstairs are 3 bedrooms, including a primary suite featuring a walk-in closet and updated bathroom. The finished basement offers versatile living space and ample storage, ideal for hobbies, a home gym, or expanding your living area. Outside, you’ll love the sprawling fenced-in yard and large deck that provides the perfect setting for gatherings and outdoor entertainment. This convenient location allows easy access to major highways like 495, as well as a plethora of restaurants, shopping options including Market Basket, and other conveniences all just moments away. Central A/C and gas heat are added perks! Open Houses Fri, Sat, & Sun
